lead_paragraph: Northampton Saints will not allow winger George North to play again until he undergoes an independent medical assessment on the head injury he suffered against Leicester Tigers on Saturday.

headline.print_headline: North Stood Down From Playing by Northampton Over Head Injury Concerns
